<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">“In God we trust” is the national motto.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id74501806-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(<ref href="/us/pl/105/225">Pub. L. 105–225</ref>, <date date="1998-08-12">Aug. 12, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/1263">112 Stat. 1263</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/107/293/s3/a">Pub. L. 107–293, § 3(a)</ref>, <date date="2002-11-13">Nov. 13, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/2060">116 Stat. 2060</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
