<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id7450180b-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2002—<ref href="/us/pl/107/293">Pub. L. 107–293</ref> reenacted section catchline and text without change.</p>
